\rm \begin{eqnarray}\rm Let\ \ a &=&\rm 2n\!+\!r\\ \rm for\  \ \ r&\in& \{0,1\}\ \end{eqnarray}\!\bigg\rbrace\:\Rightarrow\: \bigg\lfloor \dfrac{a^2}2\bigg\rfloor = \bigg\lfloor 2n^2\!+2nr+\dfrac{r^2}2\bigg\rfloor =\, 2n^2\!+\!2nr,\,\ 
\rm\ \ \dfrac{r^2}2 \in\bigg\{0,\,\dfrac{1}2\!\bigg\}
